  "notes": "40V synchronous NVDC quasi dual-phase buck-boost battery charge controller for 2- to 5-cell Li-Ion/LiFePO4 batteries. Optimized for GaN HEMT. Charges up to 16.3A/30A (5mΩ/2mΩ sense). Input current limit up to 8.2A/16.4A (10mΩ/5mΩ sense). 600kHz/800kHz programmable switching frequency. 36-pin WQFN (4.0mm x 5.0mm). Supports USB-C PD EPR, SPR, and legacy adapters. Pass-through mode for >99% efficiency. Dual random spread spectrum (DRSS) for EMI compliance. IMVP8/IMVP9 compliant with PROCHOT and PSYS. 16-bit ADC for voltage/current/power monitoring.",
